trans-unit.source: Enumeration of activity result values that qualifies the state of an <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity"></xref> that has an <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionStatus"></xref> of <xref uid="langword_csharp_Closed" name="Closed" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Enumeração de valores de resultado de atividade que qualifica o estado de um <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity"> </xref> que tem um <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionStatus"> </xref> de <xref uid="langword_csharp_Closed" name="Closed" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] Result represents the final status of an <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity> instance within a workflow instance.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]Resultado representa o status final de um <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity>instância em uma instância de fluxo de trabalho.</xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity>

trans-unit.source: The values of the enumeration are based upon the activity state diagram that is determined by the activity-engine contract.
trans-unit.target: Os valores da enumeração baseiam-se um diagrama de estado de atividade que é determinado pelo contrato de mecanismo de atividade.

trans-unit.source: Values other than None are allowed only for an activity whose <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionStatus> is <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionStatus>.
trans-unit.target: Diferente de None são permitidos valores apenas para uma atividade cuja <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionStatus>é <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionStatus>.</xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionStatus> </xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionStatus>

trans-unit.source: The activity has transitioned to the closed state from the canceling state.
trans-unit.target: A atividade tiver feito a transição para o estado closed do estado de cancelamento.

trans-unit.source: The activity has transitioned to the closed state from the compensating state.
trans-unit.target: A atividade tiver feito a transição para o estado closed do estado de compensação.

trans-unit.source: The activity has transitioned to the closed state from the faulting state.
trans-unit.target: A atividade tiver feito a transição para o estado closed do estado com falha.

trans-unit.source: The activity is not in the <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionStatus.Closed> state.
The activity has transitioned to the closed state from the executing state.
trans-unit.target: A atividade tiver feito a transição para o estado closed do estado de execução.

trans-unit.source: The activity has transitioned to the closed state from the initialized state.
trans-unit.target: A atividade tiver feito a transição para o estado closed do estado inicializado.
